00:08:51.019 --> 00:08:54.460
We see that Jehovah's name clearly is in the Hebrew text.

00:08:54.460 --> 00:08:57.980
So quotations are made from the Hebrew Bible.

00:08:57.980 --> 00:09:00.059
They should be there in the Greek text as well.

00:09:00.860 --> 00:09:07.019
So by Jehovah's people being honest in trying to do what they see needs to be done,

00:09:07.019 --> 00:09:11.820
no matter what the world may offer as an opinion, that builds confidence as well in the

00:09:11.820 --> 00:09:17.580
translation. When we see how the New World translation really holds Jehovah's name up on high,

00:09:18.379 --> 00:09:23.580
that warms our hearts and helps us to get to know Jehovah's as a person and as a friend.

