accurate as possible. I have never discovered in the New World translation any biased intent to

00:09:43.340 --> 00:09:50.220
read something into the text that it does not contain. The most scholarly Bible ever produced

00:09:50.220 --> 00:09:57.019
is the New World Translation Reference Edition of 1984, containing the most advanced study aids.

